MERCURIES LIFE said unconsolidated sales
in August fell 37.80% to NT$5,928,783,000 from NT$9,531,688,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  8/2011           8/2010
Sales           5,928,783        9,531,688   
YOY%             -37.80%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           72,094,069       78,005,112  
YOY%              -7.58% 
=================================================================
 